SECTION 7 — APPS SCRIPT REDEPLOYMENT (When code changes)
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

WHEN TO REDEPLOY:
──────────────────
  → Whenever you download a new script version
  → Whenever you change the SECRET_TOKEN
  → Whenever itKINS sends you a script update

HOW TO REDEPLOY APPS SCRIPT:
──────────────────────────────
  1. Open Google Sheet → Extensions → Apps Script
  2. Select ALL code (Ctrl+A) → Delete
  3. Admin → Setup → Download Script v5
  4. Open downloaded file → Copy all text
  5. Paste into Apps Script editor
  6. Click Save (Ctrl+S)
  7. Click "Deploy" button (top right)
  8. Click "Manage Deployments"
  9. Click pencil/edit icon on your existing deployment
  10. Version: Select "New Version"
  11. Click "Deploy"
  12. Copy the NEW /exec URL (it may be the same or different)
  13. Update APPS_SCRIPT_URL in your React code if URL changed

IMPORTANT:
  → Always use "New Version" not "Update existing"
  → Old URL usually stays the same
  → If URL changes, update React code immediately


