──────────────────────
  Scan barcode     → Just scan, auto-adds to cart
  Search item      → Type in search box
  Arrow Up/Down    → Navigate search results
  Enter            → Select highlighted item / confirm qty
  Escape           → Clear search / go back to search from qty
  Arrow Up/Down    → In qty box: increase/decrease quantity

CALCULATOR SHORTCUTS:
──────────────────────
  0-9              → Numbers
  + - * /          → Operations  
  Enter or =       → Calculate result
  Backspace        → Delete last digit
  C                → Clear all
  Escape           → Close calculator

LOGIN SCREEN SHORTCUTS:
────────────────────────
  Type numbers     → Goes directly to PIN
  Backspace        → Delete PIN digit
  Enter            → Login


